[[伊利諾州|伊利諾州]][[索傑_(伊利諾州)|索傑村]]的[[鐵門灰熊隊|鐵門灰熊]]棒球隊自2006年5月起，開始在他們的[[棒球場|球場]]供應路德漢堡<ref name="ESPN" />。他們的版本以[[Krispy_Kreme|Krispy Kreme]]糖霜甜甜圈為基底，包裹[[安格斯牛|黑安格斯]]全牛肉餅，再搭配微熔起司和兩片培根肉。它被美國人暱稱為「[[心臟內科|心臟科醫師]]的噩夢」，每份的熱量高達1000[[卡路里|大卡]]（4200千焦耳），並含有約45克的脂肪<ref name="ESPN" />。路德漢堡很快地成為球場的熱銷美食，成功為球場帶來人潮和錢潮，[[ESPN|ESPN]]網站甚至形容鐵門灰熊球場是「靠卡路里吸引人氣」<ref name="ESPN">{{cite web |author=Darren Rovell |title=Illinois team counts on calories to draw attention |url=http://sports.espn.go.com/mlb/news/story?id=2362369 |work=[[ESPN|ESPN.com]] |date=2006-03-10 |accessdate=2011-08-05 |archive-date=2011-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110809101252/http://sports.espn.go.com/mlb/news/story?id=2362369 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。然而，它也招致不少「漢堡純粹主義者」的批評，也有許多人因為健康考量或對其口感的想像而打消品嘗路德漢堡的念頭<ref name="abcnews20060623">{{cite news |title=Ballpark Burger Adds Krispy Kremes to the Mix |first=Jessica |last=Golden |first2=Lynda |last2=Figueredo |url=http://abcnews.go.com/US/Story?id=2113470 |publisher=[[ABC_News|ABC News]] |location=[[New_York_City|New York City]], [[United_States|United States]] |date=2006-06-23 |accessdate=2010-10-19 |quote=An All-Beef Patty With Cheese, Bacon on Krispy Kreme Donut Buns |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5tbKizk1S?url=http://abcnews.go.com/US/Story?id=2113470 |archivedate=2010-10-19 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

紐約[[皇后區|皇后區]][[亞斯托里亞|亞斯托里亞]]的一家[[黎巴嫩|黎巴嫩]]漢堡店則販售一款特別的路德漢堡。漢堡店店長因為他的朋友在[[美國南部|美國南部]]旅遊時嘗到路德漢堡，而得到靈感，在2010年開始供應以火雞肉培根製成、[[符合教規的食物_(伊斯蘭教)|符合伊斯蘭教規]]的路德漢堡（Crave甜甜圈漢堡）。他們的漢堡重約0.25磅（0.11公斤）、定價6.50美元，在[[紐約市|紐約市]]獨樹一格，每天約可賣出10到20份。<ref name="nydn20100707">{{cite news |title=Try this burger with bacon and cheese served on a sugary doughnut bun, but no lard included |first=Erica |last=Pearson |url=http://www.nydailynews.com/ny_local/queens/2010/07/07/2010-07-07_wait_its_a_burger_with_bun_made_of_doughnut_and_comes_with_bacon_but_no_side_of_.html |newspaper=[[紐約每日新聞|Daily News]] |publisher=Mortimer Zuckerman |location=[[New_York_City|New York City]], USA |date=2010-07-07 |accessdate=2010-11-02 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5tx7N06BV?url=http://www.nydailynews.com/ny_local/queens/2010/07/07/2010-07-07_wait_its_a_burger_with_bun_made_of_doughnut_and_comes_with_bacon_but_no_side_of_.html |archivedate=2010-11-03 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

